CS_theluckylastman

 Instalation:Just extract the archive to CSS folder. You know...
 
########Made by costy alias the_ghost###############
 NOTE:I worked at that map 3-4 days, because is my second map :D
It contains some secrets...
 The story: In a bad day, when is raining, a group of terrorists have
captured some people from a house. They killed all the hostages! But there's 
a lucky man! He survived! You must rescure the lucky last man!
 Objectives:
-CTs = Rescure the lucky last man!
-Terrorists = Prevent CTs to rescure the last hostage!
